#######################################
# Repository Management API
#######################################

### [2.1] List All Repositories
GET {{baseUrl}}/repositories
Content-Type: application/json

### [2.2] Get Repository Details
GET {{baseUrl}}/repositories/{{repositoryId}}
Content-Type: application/json

